{"tid":624230,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[I LOVE 星座] 平時都唔信星座,但事實擺在眼前就真係唔到我唔信","createTime":"2018-04-10T16:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T18:43:01.000Z","uid":157510,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1ef20224974cfe4239f062854bc2bc570dc73c3d","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    : 星座占卜師<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n話說小弟依期頭頭踫著黑所以就諗住去轉廟街睇個相<br />\n<br />\n點知一去到廟街就俾個用黑布包到自己實一實既神秘東方女子攔住<br />\n<br />\n我一睇佢包裝就知道肯定係D乜野星座占卜師<br />\n<br />\n利申小弟從來都唔信依類無科學根據既迷信嘢,尤其係星座<br />\n<br />\n所以我就好客氣咁婉拒咗佢<br />\n<br />\n但點知佢仲係唔死心,猛咁扯住我件杉唔俾我走<br />\n<br />\n我即刻就興過火屎,對住佢大喝一句[你啲星座撚食屎啦,我金牛座唔見我發達?]<br />\n<br />\n可能係因為我太霸氣,嚇到佢停咗喺原地呆咗5秒先回到神<br />\n<br />\n本來以為佢就此作罷,但估唔到佢接住落嚟會講依句嘢<br />\n<br />\n[唔好再話星座學係迷信,我可以用星座嚟測智商,但你首先要講&quot;我信星座&quot;依四隻字,唔係會唔靈]<br />\n<br />\n我見佢咁有信心咪附和下佢囉,講咗嗰句&quot;我信星座&quot;出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :  ........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  : 信星座既都係弱智仔<br />\n<br />\n中咗....我智商真係得80,今次真係不得不佩服星座依樣嘢"},{"pid":"b2ba84635bcc561b8d390630cfb383345f86fd35","tid":624230,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f3596b3d70d300c2409932a194a61024f55acb","tid":624230,"uid":177924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"80/100"},{"pid":"9f6db635b2df27858cb8fce6db7f13971562bd57","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aa86dd6ead27c8af2ff21def0d9833295ccf5a","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T03:58:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411f7acade68629a861f7af8e6b9be382d337a4d","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T08:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf757c878c03167d2b2ecd5205d94bb9a726f68","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T09:34:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7934a1b616934bd80b245f2ee4b278d21470b93","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T10:48:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1b157c8f808726b427460089a71764b2e3792d","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7944abd63b351106cfa0ca9f27c2acff463bd83e","tid":624230,"uid":116157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"699cca5ccb3869f4b3390cceaf37b3a2d988d3a3","tid":624230,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"短啲會好啲"},{"pid":"dc92ed4f4aebae1da4ef089cd8ddff3acf1d84da","tid":624230,"uid":157510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"699cca5ccb3869f4b3390cceaf37b3a2d988d3a3","tid":624230,"uid":37713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"短啲會好啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201